{"id":301921,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virgin_Islands_at_the_Olympics","text":"The United States Virgin Islands has been in 9 Summer Olympic Games. They have also been in the Winter Olympic Games 7 times. Peter Holmberg took second place in sailing at the 1988 Summer Olympics.\nThe Virgin Islands Olympic Committee was formed in 1967 and recognized by the IOC the same year.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"United_States_Virgin_Islands","surface_form":"United States Virgin Islands","offset":4},{"uri":"Summer_Olympic_Games","surface_form":"Summer Olympic Games","offset":47},{"uri":"Winter_Olympic_Games","surface_form":"Winter Olympic Games","offset":96},{"uri":"Peter_Holmberg","surface_form":"Peter Holmberg","offset":126},{"uri":"Sailing","surface_form":"sailing","offset":162},{"uri":"1988_Summer_Olympics","surface_form":"1988 Summer Olympics","offset":177},{"uri":"Recognize","surface_form":"recognized","offset":259},{"uri":"IOC","surface_form":"IOC","offset":277}]}